m%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1536-andre-russell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndre%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20yet%20again%20at%20his%20explosive%20best%20as%20the%20KKR%20batters%20made%20short%20work%20of%20the%20DC%20bowling%20attack.%20While%20KKR%20fell%20short%20of%20beating%20the%20highest%20IPL%20score%20of%20all%20time%20-%20277%2F3%20-%20that%20belongs%20to%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20this%20was%20the%20highest%20total%20posted%20by%20a%20side%20away%20from%20home%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighest%20score%20by%20an%20IPL%20side%20at%20an%20away%20ground%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20vs%20Delhi%20Capitals%20-%20IPL%202024%20(Vizag)%20-%20272%2F7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow%20Super%20Giants%20vs%20Punjab%20Kings%20-%20IPL%202023%20(Mohali)%20-%20257%2F5%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20vs%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20-%20IPL%202024%20(Hyderabad)%20-%20246%2F5%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20vs%20Punjab%20Kings%20-%20IPL%202018%20(Indore)%20-%20245%2F6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%20vs%20Punjab%20Kings%20-%20IPL%202008%20(Mohali)%20-%20240%2F5%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKKR's%20herculean%20target%20of%20273%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20too%20much%20for%20the%20DC%20as%20they%20gave%20in%20to%20the%20pressure%20and%20ended%20up%20suffering%20a%20106-run%20defeat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20duo%20of%20Mitchell%20Starc%20and%20Vaibhav%20Arora%20bagged%20two%20wickets%20each%20to%20reduce%20DC%20to%2033%2F4%20in%20the%20powerplay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20blow%20derailed%20DC's%20approach%20to%20chasing%20down%20the%20massive%20total%20which%20got%20more%20challenging%20with%20each%20delivery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(55)%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs%20(54)%20bought%20up%20a%2093-run%20stand%20with%20some%20effortless%20power%20hitting%20and%20gave%20the%20home%20fans%20something%20to%20cheer%20about.%20'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20scored%20back-to-back%20half-centuries%20in%20the%20IPL%20showcasing%20signs%20of%20him%20returning%20to%20his%20prime%20form.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20Pant's%20dismissal%2C%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%20for%20DC%20as%20they%20ended%20up%20losing%20the%20game%20with%20a%20massive%20margin%20of%20106%20runs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKKR%20marched%20on%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20table%20with%20their%20third%20consecutive%20win%20of%20the%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20innings%2C%20the%20'City%20of%20Destiny'%20witnessed%20two%20hours%20of%20carnage%2C%202%20hours%20of%20ruthless%20ball-striking%20and%20120%20minutes%20of%20torture%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20bowlers%20as%20Narine%20(85)%2C%20Raghuvanshi%20(54)%2C%20Russell%20(41)%20and%20Rinku%20Singh's%20brutal-bashing%20helped%20KKR%20come%20within%20touching%20distance%20of%20surpassing%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20score%20of%20277%2C%20however%20Kolkata%20ended%20up%20with%20the%20second-highest%20total%20in%20the%20IPL%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20the%20toss%20and%20opting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20KKR%20got%20off%20to%20a%20rollicking%20start%20with%20a%20fiery%20partnership%20between%20Philip%20Salt%20and%20Sunil%20Narine.%20Having%20not%20grabbed%20a%20single%20run%20in%20the%20first%20over%20delivered%20by%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%2C%20Salt%20hammered%20Ishant%20Sharma%20for%20back-to-back%20two%20boundaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20KKR%20openers%20finally%20saw%20through%20Khaleel%20Ahmed's%20trend%20of%20keeping%20his%20deliveries%20furthest%20away%20from%20the%20wicket.%20Narine%20ran%20an%20onslaught%20during%20Ishant's%20second%20over%20and%20punished%20the%20DC%20bowler%20immensely%20as%20he%20bagged%2026%20runs%20in%20the%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDropped%20on%20one%20and%20caught%20on%20second%2C%20Salt's%20innings%20came%20to%20an%20end%20after%20he%20got%20dismissed%20by%20Anrich%20Nortje%2C%20following%20a%20phenomenal%20backward-running%20catch%20from%20Tristan%20Stubbs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20bowlers%20continued%20to%20miss%20the%20mark%20against%20Narine%20and%20the%20opener%20completed%20his%20second%20fifty%20of%20IPL%202024%20within%20just%2021%20balls.%20However%2C%20Nortje%20provided%20DC%20with%20a%20massive%20breakthrough%2C%20removing%20Salt%20for%2018%2C%20but%20it%20was%20Narine%20who%20got%20everyone's%20attention%20with%20an%20explosive%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarine%20with%20his%20batting%20fireworks%20that%20witnessed%20the%20side%20complete%20their%20100-run%20mark%20within%20just%207.3%20overs%20into%20the%20game%2C%20alongside%20Raghuvanshi%20looked%20destructive%20at%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitchell%20Marsh%20came%20into%20the%20attack%20to%20stop%20the%20onslaught%20by%20KKR%2C%20as%20Narine%20and%20Raghuvanshi%20opted%20for%20a%20more%20controlled%20approach%20to%20see%20through%20the%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20Raghuvanshi%20just%20cannot%20stop%20impressing%20the%20cricket%20fraternity%2C%20as%20he%20added%20up%20to%20his%20impressive%20performance%20in%20the%20match%20with%20a%20sensational%20reverse%20six.%20The%20youngster%20then%20slammed%20his%20maiden%20IPL%20half-century%20with%20Narine%20in%20a%20destructive%20mood%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20duo%20completed%20their%20100-run%20partnership%20with%20significant%20ease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20phenomenal%20Narine%20innings%20came%20to%20an%20end%2C%20much%20to%20the%20ultimate%20relief%20of%20the%20DC%20bowling%20unit%20until%20Marsh%20got%20the%20big%20wicket.%20Narine%20went%20back%20to%20the%20pavilion%20after%20scoring%2085%20off%20just%2039%20balls.%20Nortje%20sent%20Raghuvanshi%20packing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuvanshi%20rocked%20up%20on%20debut%20and%20delivered%20a%20stunning%20performance%20of%2054%20off%2027%20however%20his%20fine%20knock%20came%20to%20an%20end%20as%20he%20was%20sent%20packing%20by%20Nortje%20in%20the%2013.2%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2015%20overs%20into%20the%20match%2C%20KKR%20crossed%20the%20200%20mark.%20In%20the%20second-last%20over%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%20smoked%20Nortje%20for%20three%20maximums%20and%20one%20four%20before%20losing%20his%20wicket%20to%20a%20miss-timed%20shot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20terrific%20yorker%20from%20Ishant%20dismissed%20Russell%2C%20rattling%20off%20the%20wickets%20with%20a%20fiery%20pace.%20In%20the%20same%20over%20he%20removed%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20putting%20a%20stop%20to%20KKR's%20dominant%20performance%2C%20restricting%20Kolkata%20to%20272%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712197680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fuptrbs6g_sca_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Ffirst-time-ever-in-ipl-history-kkrs-mammoth-272-scripts-momentous-record-5369071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20registered%20a%20mammoth%20total%20of%20272%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20seven%20wickets%20against%20Delhi%20Capitals%20in%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta's%20WhatsApp%20back%20up%20after%20global%20outage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712197645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109019915%2Cimgsize-16430.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fmetas-whatsapp-back-up-after-global-outage%2Farticleshow%2F109019564.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta's%20WhatsApp%20resumed%20service%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20an%20hours-long%20outage%20that%20disrupted%20services%20for%20thousands%20of%20users%20worldwide.%20At%20its%20peak%2C%20over%2024%2C000%20WhatsApp%20users%20in%20the%20US%20and%205%2