0any%20claims%20of%20disrespect%20or%20mistreatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20light%20of%20the%20aforenoted%20facts%20of%20the%20present%20case%2C%20we%20find%20that%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20respondent%20(wife)%20towards%20the%20appellant%20(husband)%20has%20been%20such%20that%20it%20is%20devoid%20of%20dignity%20and%20empathy%20towards%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20such%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20one%20spouse%20towards%20the%20other%2C%20it%20brings%20disgrace%20to%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20marriage%20and%20there%20exists%20no%20possible%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20he%20should%20be%20compelled%20to%20live%20while%20enduring%20the%20agony%20of%20living%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20scrutinized%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Mr%20Kapur's%20wife%2C%20highlighting%20the%20rapid%20professional%20success%20achieved%20by%20him%20within%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%20This%20success%2C%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20is%20indicative%20of%20his%20dedication%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20casting%20doubt%20on%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20allegations%20levied%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20concluded%20that%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Mr%20Kapur's%20wife%20lacked%20substantiation%20and%20were%20aimed%20at%20tarnishing%20his%20reputation.%20Such%20unfounded%20claims%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20constitute%20cruelty%20and%20have%20a%20detrimental%20impact%20on%20one's%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20estranged%20couple%20got%20married%20in%20April%202008%20and%20have%20a%20son%20born%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712195160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffgbcscjo_kunal-kapur_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchef-kunal-kapur-alleges-wife-disrespected-parents-she-says-h