nted%20at%20a%20probable%20end%20to%20its%20crisis%2C%20saying%20the%20flight%20schedules%20are%20expected%20to%20normalise%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20pilots%20have%20pointed%20to%20fatigue%20issues%20which%20could%20have%20direct%20safety%20ramifications.%20%26quot%3BPilots%20are%20flying%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20their%20maximum%20flight%20duty%20limitations.%20This%20is%20causing%20major%20health%20issues%20and%20everyone%20falling%20sick%20frequently%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20saw%20a%20surge%20in%20flight%20cancellations%20as%20the%20airline%20struggled%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20pilots.%20An%20increasing%20number%20of%20its%20pilots%20have%20called%20in%20sick%2C%20protesting%20a%20revised%20salary%20structure%20ahead%20of%20the%20full-service%20carrier's%20merger%20with%20Tata-owned%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20%26quot%3Bcoordinating%20together%20and%20taking%20mass%20sick%20leave%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20just%20tired%20from%20flying.%20The%20new%20FDTL%20(Flight%20Duty%20Time%20Limitations)%20rules%20should%20have%20given%20us%20some%20relief%20but%20as%20expected%20that%20is%20also%20not%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20or%20DGCA%20deferred%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20revised%20flight%20duty%20norms%20for%20pilots%20that%20were%20to%20be%20effective%20from%20June%201.%20The%20revised%20norms%20have%20reportedly%20been%20deferred%20for%20some%20time%20to%20have%20wider%20consultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20norms%20provide%20for%20more%20rest%20time%20for%20pilots%20and%20seek%20to%20alleviate%20pilot%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20officials%20in%20the%20airline%2C%20including%20CEO%20Vinod%20Kannan%20and%20senior%20members%20of%20his%20management%20team%2C%20held%20a%20virtual%20town%20hall%20with%20striking%20pilots%20Wednesday%20evening%20where%20discussions%20were%20held%20on%20new%20contracts%20and%20rostering%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompany%20sources%20said%20the%20pilots%20had%20been%20promised%20a%20course%20correction%20to%20address%20concerns%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20merger%20with%20Air%20India.%20This%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20will%20include%20improved%20growth%20potential%20once%20the%20merger%20is%20complete%20and%20better%20rostering%20of%20pilots%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20by%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlagging%20major%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bflying%20at%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20maximum%20duty%20limitations%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20pilot%20sources%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20falling%20sick%20frequently.%20Pilots%20are%20already%20exceeding%20their%20max%20sick%20leaves%20in%20a%20year%20and%20ending%20up%20in%20leave%20without%20pay%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20criticised%20the%20airline%20for%20%26quot%3Btrusting%20software%20more%20than%20their%20pilots%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BPilots%20have%20been%20complaining%20about%20fatigue%20to%20the%20management.%20Management%20relies%20on%20the%20Boeing%20Alertness%20Model%20(BAM)%20and%20says%20the%20flight%20is%20safe%2C%20so%20you%20should%20have%20nothing%20to%20complain%20about.%20They%20trust%20software%20more%20than%20their%20pilots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20is%20%26quot%3Bangry%20at%20the%20new%20contract%2C%20but%20we%20all%20knew%20it%20was%20coming%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20company%20sources%20said%20that%20almost%20100%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20pilots%20accepted%20the%20new%20contract.%20Pilots%20expressed%20no%20protest%20during%20the%20virtual%20town%20hall%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20had%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20was%20forced%20to%20cut%20a%20number%20of%20flights%20due%20to%20the%20pilot%20shortage%20and%20was%20using%20some%20of%20its%20larger%20aircraft%20to%20%26quot%3Baccommodate%20more%20passengers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20sources%20said%20only%2024%20flights%20were%20cancelled%20Wednesday%20compared%20to%20the%2052%20a%20day%20before%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPilots%20have%20been%20complaining%20that%20their%20cost%20to%20company%20(CTC)%20had%20been%20reduced%20in%20the%20new%20contract%2C%20in%20which%20they%20are%20mandated%20to%20fly%2040%20hours%20as%20opposed%20to%2070%20hours%20earlier.%20Sources%2C%20however%2C%20said%20under%20the%20new%20structure%20pilots%20were%20incentivised%20to%20fly%20more%2C%20and%20could%20earn%20more%20than%20they%20did%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20said%20yesterday%20it%20was%20monitoring%20the%20developments%20while%20the%20aviation%20regulator%20sought%20daily%20information%20on%20flight%20disruptions%20from%20Vistara.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712194920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flbr0oo6_vistara_625x300_07_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilots-flag-burnout-as-vistara-hopes-for-end-to-crisis-by-weekend-sources-5369341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20Vistara%20hinted%20at%20a%20probable%20end%20to%20its%20crisis%2C%20saying%20the%20flight%20schedules%20are%20expected%20to%20normalise%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20pilots%20have%20pointed%20to%20fatigue%20issues%20which%20could%20have%20direct%20safety%20ramifications.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilots-flag-burnout-as-vistara-hopes-for-end-to-crisis-by-weekend-sources-5369341%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilots-flag-burnout-as-vistara-hopes-for-end-to-crisis-by-weekend-sources-5369341%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilots-flag-burnout-as-vistara-hopes-for-e