y%2C%20and%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20shopping%20at%20Trader%20Joe's%20not%20only%20because%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-bananas-raise-price-are-no-longer-19-cents-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20prices%20on%20staples%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20fun%20new%20items%20to%20try.%20Knowing%20that%20these%20new%20items%20may%20sometimes%20be%20the%20result%20of%20dealings%20that%20could%20squeeze%20a%20small%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20that%20does%20not%20feel%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-smaller-ethnic-food-brands-private-label-accused-dupe-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712181775000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660dc8973f923f7dab046834%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-smaller-ethnic-food-brands-private-label-accused-dupe-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Smaller%20food%20companies%20say%20after%20a%20private-labeling%20deal%20fell%20through%2C%20Trader%20Joe's%20made%20a%20dupe%2C%20a%20new%20story%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-smaller-ethnic-food-brands-private-label-accused-dupe-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Will%20Trent%E2%80%99%20Renewed%20for%20Season%203%20at%20ABC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712181600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWill-Trent.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235959774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CWill%20Trent%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20renewed%20for%20Season%203%20