aid%20that%20he%20would%20leave%20the%20country%20if%20Modi%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20is%20now%20saying%20that%20he%20has%20an%20inseparable%20bond%20with%20Modi.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20politicians%20should%20have%20ideological%20clarity%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20further%20said%20that%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20are%20against%20social%20justice.%20Therefore%20they%20do%20not%20like%20reservations.%20Reservation%20is%20not%20alms.%20It%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20oppressed%20communities.%20Reservation%20should%20exist%20as%20long%20as%20the%20caste%20system%20exists%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBefore%20independence%20and%20the%20British%20period%2C%20did%20we%2C%20the%20Shudras%20have%20the%20right%20to%20study%3F%20Did%20women%20have%20any%20rights%3F%20A%20woman%20had%20to%20burn%20herself%20alive%20immediately%20after%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%20Such%20inhuman%20practices%20inspired%20by%20Manusmriti%20were%20prohibited%20by%20our%20constitution.%20Therefore%2C%20they%20want%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20Manusmirthi%20by%20making%20amendments%20to%20the%20constitution.%20The%20CM%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20understand%20this%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShudras%2C%20Dalits%20and%20women%20are%20not%20allowed%20inside%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20Senior%20BJP%20leaders%20like%20Nanje%20Gowda%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Gulihatti%20Shekhar%20have%20also%20openly%20said%20that%20they%20were%20not%20allowed%20inside%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20RSS.%20This%20is%20the%20truth.%20The%20Shudras%20are%20just%20being%20used.%20Therefore%2C%20Shudras%2C%20Dalits%20and%20women%20should%20not%20join%20to%20RSS%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20asked%20'Should%20we%20not%20criticise%20the%20JDS%20which%20has%20now%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20RSS%3F%20Congress%20passed%20the%20law%20to%20allocate%20money%20in%20the%20budget%20according%20to%20the%20Dalit%20population.%20Our%20government%20has%20enacted%20a%20law%20that%2024.1%20per%20cent%20of%20development%20funds%20should%20be%20set%20aside.%20This%20progressive%20law%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20by%20any%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20country.%20Only%20our%20Congress%20government%20has%20done%20it.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20community%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20all%20these%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20that%20it%20was%20our%20Congress%20government%20that%20implemented%20reservations%20for%20Dalits%20in%20contracts.%20Is%20it%20not%20the%20same%20BJP%20that%20opposed%20the%20Mandal%20report%20and%20the%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%3F%20The%20SCP%2F%20TSP%20Act%20was%20enacted%20by%20the%20Congress%20Government.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20CM%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20make%20Congress%20candidate%20M.%20Laxman%20win%2C%20instead%20of%20supporting%20those%20who%20provoke%20them%20emotionally%20and%20threaten%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20Welfare%20Minister%20HC%20Mahadevappa%2C%20KPCC%20Working%20President%20Tanveer%20Seth%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20Laxman%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20wing%20of%20KPCC%20were%20present%20on%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20will%20have%20elections%20in%20two%20phases%20on%20April%2026%20and%20May%207%20for%2028%20constituencies.%20The%20general%20election%20for%20543%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20will%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20phases%20starting%20April%2019%2C%20with%20counting%20to%20be%20held%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712181300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4dl8iq5g_siddaramaiah_625x300_03_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht