n-unveils-chemicals-company-solvay-as-top-investment-idea.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholds%20a%20top-five%20spot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSolvay%20is%20a%20commodity%20chemical%20company%20with%20a%20relatively%20high%20and%20stable%20margin%2C%20a%20high%20return%20on%20capital%20and%20a%20good%20return%20of%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20Einhorn%20outlined%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20this%20boring%20essential%20chemicals%20business%20will%20generate%20attractive%20risk-adjusted%20returns%20for%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20sent%20Solvay's%20American%20depository%20receipts%20soaring%2018%25%20to%20%243.22%20apiece%20at%202%3A45%20p.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20large%20part%2C%20the%20company%20focuses%20on%20manufacturing%20soda%20ash%2C%20a%20common%20compound%20used%20to%20produce%20everything%20from%20glass%2C%20soaps%2C%20to%20lithium%20batteries.%20Though%20soda%20ash%20is%20not%20a%20volatile%20commodity%2C%20COVID%20distortions%20have%20pulled%20down%20its%20capacity%20utilization%2C%20with%202024%20set%20to%20be%20a%20trough%20year%2C%20Einhorn%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20Solvay's%20ties%20to%20soda%20ash%2C%20many%20sell-side%20analysts%20have%20printed%20mostly%20negative%20reviews%20of%20the%20company%2C%20he%20cited.%20But%20these%20reports%20have%20largely%20ignored%20the%20fact%20that%2070%25%20of%20Solvay's%20revenue%20streams%20come%20from%20other%20chemical%20products%2C%20including%20peroxides%2C%20silica%20and%20coatis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20point%20I'm%20making%20is%20that%20while%20there%20is%20a%20reduction%20in%20soda%20ash%20prices%20and%20profits%20in%202024%2C%20which%20everyone%20knows%20about%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20business%20is%20less%20cyclical%20and%20more%20resilient%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bears%20seem%20intent%20on%20completely%20ignoring%20that%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3