C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20launched%20a%20social%20networking%20venture%20called%20Threads%20in%20July%202023%2C%20leveraging%20Instagram's%20audience%20to%20build%20a%20new%20microblogging%20site%20to%20compete%20with%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20Meta's%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Threads%20app%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20of%20Meta's%20Threads%20app%20is%20to%20read%20and%20engage%20in%20public%20conversations.%20On%20Threads%2C%20users%20can%20post%20a%20%26quot%3Bthread%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0usually%20a%20short%20piece%20of%20text%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20users%20can%20%26quot%3Blike%2C%26quot%3B%20repost%2C%20or%20reply%20to%20the%20thread.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Threads%20app%20was%20built%20by%20Instagram%2C%20and%20requires%20an%20Instagram%20account%20to%20connect%2C%20though%20you'll%20have%20to%20download%20the%20Threads%20standalone%20app%20separately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20photo-%20and%20video-based%2C%20Threads%20is%20a%20predominantly%20text-based%20social-networking%20platform%2C%20though%20users%20can%20also%20post%20media%20files%20like%20photos%2C%20links%2C%20and%20short%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThreads%20posts%20can%20be%20up%20to%20500%20characters%2C%20and%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20privacy%20settings%2C%20your%20posts%20can%20either%20be%20seen%20by%20anyone%20on%20the%20Threads%20interface%20or%20just%20your%20approved%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20and%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20stories%20feature%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Threads%20does%20not%20show%20who%20has%20viewed%20your%20profile%20or%20your%20posts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20launched%20Threads%20in%20July%202023%2C%20but%20not%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Back%20when%20Meta%20was%20known%20only%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20released%20a%20previous%20version%20of%20Threads%20in%202019.%20That%20initial%20version%20was%20a%20messaging%20app%20geared%20at%20competing%20with%20Snapchat%2C%20but%20it%20never%20gained%20much%20traction%20and%20was%20discontinued%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThreads%20vs.%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20number%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%94%20like%20BlueSky%2C%20Mastodon%2C%20and%20Truth%20Social%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20have%20tried%20to%20unseat%20X%20as%20the%20top%20social%20media%20app%20for%20public%20discourse%2C%20only%20Threads%20has%20had%20much%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThreads%20was%20launched%20at%20a%20highly%20opportune%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20over%20Twitter%20in%20October%202022%2C%20renamed%20it%20X%2C%20and%20began%20implementing%20a%20number%20of%20unpopular%20changes%20that%20caused%20many%20users%20to%20threaten%20to%20abandon%20ship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Meta%20released%20Threads%2C%20it%20was%20able%20to%20use%20Instagram's%20existing%20user%20base%20to%20quickly%20garner%20downloads%20and%20gain%20a%20foothold.%20Threads%20also%20gives%20users%20the%20option%20to%20follow%20accounts%20they%20already%20follow%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-how-metas-threads-app-compares-to-twitter-zuckerberg-elon-musk2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThreads%20and%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20share%20some%20popular%20features.%20Like%20X's%20%26quot%3BFor%20You%26quot%3B%20page%2C%20Threads%20displays%20posts%20in%20a%20long%20feed%20on%20the%20homepage.%20This%20feed%20features%20posts%20from%20accounts%20users%20follow%2C%20and%20accounts%20they%20don't%20follow%20but%20may%20be%20interested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20X%2C%20Threads%20also%20has%20a%20character%20limit%20on%20posts.%20But%20unlike%20X%2C%20Threads%20gives%20users%20500%20characters.%20X%20users%20are%20limited%20to%20280%20characters%2C%20unless%20they%20subscribe%20to%20Twitter%20Blue%20for%20%248%20a%20month%2C%20in%20which%20case%20they%20get%2025%2C000%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20an%20update%20to%20Threads%20that%20made%20the%20app%20even%20more%20similar%20to%20X%3A%20A%20%26quot%3BTrending%20Now%26quot%3B%20feature%20to%20better%20circulate%20popular%20and%20widely%20discussed%20topics%20and%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20content%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20of%20a%20phone%20with%20the%20Threads%20and%20Instagram%20logos%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a686c24cc8540019cb8885%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20Threads%20first%20launched%2C%20users%20complained%20because%20they%20realized%20they%20couldn't%20delete%20their%20Threads%20accounts%20without%20also%20deleting%20their%20Instagram%20accounts.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FGetty%20Images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThreads%20initially%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-threads-meta-instagram-privacy-zuckerberg-browser-app