%20senior%20leader%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20for%20six%20years%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Banti-party%20statements%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Earlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20party%20had%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20list%20of%20star%20campaigners%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20sources%20had%20said%20that%20a%20proposal%20to%20expel%20him%20was%20being%20prepared%20by%20the%20state%20unit%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20was%20made%20after%20Mr%20Nirupam%20made%20a%20string%20of%20remarks%20against%20Congress'%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20and%20its%20leader%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20after%20it%20announced%20some%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20including%20the%20North%20West%20Mumbai%20seat%2C%20which%20was%20reportedly%20being%20eyed%20by%20the%20Congress%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%20he%20had%20also%20made%20remarks%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20convenor%20of%20another%20party%20ally%2C%20AAP%2C%20which%20were%20not%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Congress'%20official%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20Mr%20Nirupam's%20expulsion%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BTaking%20note%20of%20the%20complaints%20of%20indiscipline%20and%20anti-party%20statements%2C%20the%20Hon'ble%20Congress%20President%20has%20approved%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Shri%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20from%20the%20party%20for%20six%20years%20with%20immediate%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20President%20Nana%20Patole%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20him%20(Mr%20Nirupam)%20off%20the%20list%20of%20star%20campaigners%20and%20have%20also%20initiated%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20him%20over%20the%20statements%20he%20made.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20was%20removed%20as%20the%20star%20campaigner%2C%20a%20defiant%20Mr%20Nirupam%20had%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20said%20he%20would%20announce%20his%20next%20course%20of%20action%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20NCP%2C%20had%20declared%20its%20list%20of%2016%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20March%2027.%20The%20list%20included%20the%20name%20of%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20-%20son%20of%20the%20sitting%20MP%20-%20for%20the%20North%20West%20Mumbai%20seat%2C%20prompting%20a%20tirade%20from%20Mr%20Nirupam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20has%20taken%20five%20seats%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20there%20is%20a%20plan%20to%20bury%20Congress%20in%20Mumbai.%20It%20seems%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20wants%20to%20force%20Congress%20to%20kneel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20constituency%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20unit%20president%20of%20the%20party%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20to%20intervene%20or%20end%20the%20alliance%20with%20Shiv%20Sena.%20If%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20thinks%20it%20can%20fight%20alone%2C%20it%20is%20making%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20over%20the%20split%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20engineered%20by%20the%20current%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Mr%20Nirupam%20called%20him%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ebachi%20kuchi%20Shiv%20Sena%20pramukh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief%20of%20what's%20left%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Mr%20Kirtikar%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20'Khichdi%20scam'%20-%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20food%20to%20migrant%20workers%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam's%20remarks%20were%20seen%20as%20adding%20to%20the%20seat-sharing%20troubles%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Announce%20Decision%20Tomorrow'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20list%20of%20star%20campaigners%2C%20Mr%20Nirupam%20had%20alluded%20to%20the%20Congress'%20accounts%20being%20frozen%20and%20said%20it%20should%20utilise%20its%20stationery%20and%20energy%20to%20save%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20leader%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20party%20should%20not%20waste%20energy%20and%20stationery%20on%20me.%20It%20should%20utilise%20the%20stationery%20and%20energy%20to%20save%20itself%20since%20the%20party%20is%20experiencing%20a%20serious%20financial%20crisis.%20The%20timeframe%20I%20had%20given%20to%20the%20party%20ends%20today.%20I%20will%20spell%20out%20my%20next%20course%20of%20action%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timeframe%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20his%20earlier%20comments%20giving%20the%20Congress%20a%20week%20to%20decide%20on%20ending%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20Mr%20Nirupam%20decide%20to%20switch%20sides%2C%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20spoilt%20for%20choice%20as%20leaders%20from%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20have%20said%20he%20would%20be%20welcome%20in%20their%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712176020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvbdovj24_sanjay-nirupam-1200_625x300_03_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%2