0while%20the%20dial%20setting%20controls%20the%20specific%20flow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatering%20wand%20or%20rain%20wand%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20long%20nozzle%20that%20helps%20extend%20water%20flow%20to%20hard-to-reach%20areas.%20It's%20usually%20controlled%20with%20a%20comfortable%20sliding%20thumb%20control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirehose%20(or%20fireman)-style%20nozzle%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20large%20dial-style%20nozzle%20that%20does%20not%20have%20a%20pistol%20grip.%20The%20spray%20patterns%20are%20not%20distinct%20and%20must%20be%20gradually%20adjusted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3EOther%20considerations%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It%20should%20be%20easy%20to%20attach%20the%20nozzle%20and%20switch%20between%20spray%20settings%2C%20if%20applicable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpray%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Your%20go-to%20garden%20tasks%20will%20dictate%20whether%20you%20need%20a%20versatile%20hose%20nozzle%20with%20various%20spray%20settings%20or%20a%20one-task%20workhorse%20like%20a%20watering%20wand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20best%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%20feature%20an%20ergonomic%20grip%20design%20that's%20comfortable%20to%20use%20for%20long%20periods.%20An%20easy-to-access%20spray%20trigger%20control%20might%20be%20better%20than%20a%20grip%20trigger%20if%20you%20have%20grip%20issues%20due%20to%20a%20condition%20like%20arthritis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Quality%20nozzles%20typically%20have%20a%20metal%20and%20rubber%20construction.%20Cheaper%20ones%20may%20contain%20plastic%20parts%20that%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20chip%20or%20break%20off%20with%20frequent%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20holding%20a%20red%20hose%20nozzle%20in%20front%20of%20fruit%20bushes%20to%20demonstrate%20our%20testing%20methodology%20for%20the%20best%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62603bebd2039d0019ba8766%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEach%20garden%20hose%20was%20put%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20to%20measure%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20comfort%2C%20spray%20distance%2C%20water%20pressure%2C%20and%20durability.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20put%20all%20the%20hose%20nozzles%20through%20these%20same%20five%20tests%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20noted%20how%20easy%20or%20difficult%20it%20was%20to%20attach%20to%20the%20hose%2C%20how%20many%20spray%20options%20it%20had%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20leaked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20noted%20if%20the%20grip%20was%20ergonomic.%20If%20the%20nozzle%20had%20a%20pistol%20grip%20design%2C%20we%20timed%20how%20long%20we%20could%20press%20the%20grip%20down%20before%20it%20got%20too%20tiring%20to%20press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpray%20distance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20concrete%2C%20we%20measured%20how%20far%20the%20nozzle%20sprayed%20water%20when%20holding%20the%20hose%20at%20a%20regular%20position%20(a%20foot%20away%20from%20the%20body).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%20pressure%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20measured%20the%20water%20pressure%20from%20the%20nozzle%20with%20a%20water%20pressure%20gauge.%20If%20there%20was%20more%20than%20one%20spray%20setting%2C%20we%20measured%20the%20low%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20high%20settings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20dropped%20each%20nozzle%20on%20concrete%20from%2010%20feet%20high%2010%20times%20and%20noted%20scuffing%2C%20scratches%2C%20abrasion%2C%20and%20any%20broken%20or%20bent%20parts.%20We%20also%20left%20the%20nozzles%20outside%20for%20two%20consecutive%20weeks%20through%20various%20weather%20conditions%2C%20including%20sun%20and%20rain%2C%20noting%20any%20rust%20and%20other%20signs%20of%20wear%20and%20tear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EGarden%20hose%20nozzle%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhy%20do%20you%20need%20a%20garden%20hose%20nozzle%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20saves%20water.%20Water%20will%20not%20come%20out%20of%20your%20hose%20unless%20you%20open%20the%20nozzle%2C%20meaning%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20run%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20the%20spigot.%20This%20is%20especially%20helpful%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20long%20hose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20garden%20hose%20nozzle%20helps%20distribute%20water%20in%20a%20more%20controlled%20manner%20than%20a%20garden%20hose%20alone.%20The%20regular%20flow%20of%20a%20garden%20hose%20alone%20isn't%20always%20the%20best%20for%20tasks%20like%20watering%20delicate%20flowers%20or%20washing%20a%20car.%20The%20different%20spray%20options%20of%20a%20nozzle%20let%20you%20customize%20the%20flow%20to%20your%20specific%20task.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20nozzle%20and%20spray%20type%20do%20you%20use%20for%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatering%20flowers%20or%20a%20vegetable%20garden%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUse%20a%20flat%20spray%20or%20shower%20delicate%20plants%20with%20a%20rain%20wand%20because%20it's%20the%20most%20gentle%20spray%20type.%20Make%20sure%20to%20water%20at%20soil%20level%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20plants.%20It's%20best%20to%20water%20them%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20before%20it%20gets%20too%20sunny%20and%20hot%2C%20so%20that%20less%20water%20will%20evaporate.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatering%20trees%20and%20shrubs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDrip%20lines%20are%20ideal%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20hose%2C%20you%20actually%20shouldn't%20use%20a%20nozzle.%20Simply%20place%20the%20hose%20on%20the%20ground%20near%20the%20tree%20and%20let%20water%20slowly%20and%20steadily%20dribble%20out.%20Rotate%20the%20hose%20around%20the%20tree%20(in%20a%20ring%20shape)%20periodically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWashing%20a%20car%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUse%20a%20jet%20spray%20with%20any%20of%20the%20nozzles%20above%20except%20the%20rain%20wand.%20If%20you're%20just%20doing%20a%20light%20rinse%2C%20a%20setting%20like%20a%20full%20shower%20could%20also%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower-washing%20a%20deck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUse%20a%20jet%20spray%20with%20any%20of%20the%20nozzles%20above%20except%20the%20rain%20wand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cp%3EWhether%20washing%20your%20dog%2C%20watering%20delicate%20plants%2C%20or%20hosing%20down%20dirt%2C%20you'll%20be%20properly%20equipped%20with%20the%20Dramm%20revolver-style%20hose%20nozzle.%20This%209-pattern%20watering%20attachment%20includes%20a%20%26quot%3Bcone%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bshower%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bmist%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bjet%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bsoaker%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bfan%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bflat%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bcenter%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bangle%26quot%3B%20spray%20pattern%2C%20so%20you'll%20have%20the%20appropriate%20option%20for%20the%20task%20in%20front%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20twist%20the%20nozzle%20to%20the%20setting%20you%20need%2C%20and%20the%20nozzle%20clicks%20to%20let%20you%20know%20you're%20ready%20to%20use%20your%20selected%20pattern.%20The%20nozzle%20reliably%20shoots%20out%20water%20when%20you%20hold%20down%20the%20trigger%20and%20doesn't%20leak%2C%20based%20on%20customer%20reviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20back%20of%20the%20nozzle%2C%20a%20wire%20lever%20lock%20keeps%20the%20'on'%20position%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20hand%20fatigue.%20The%20flow%20control%20knob%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20nozzle%20lets%20you%20adjust%20the%20pressure%20of%20each%20of%20the%209%20patterns%2C%20allowing%20for%20even%20more%20adjustability.%20The%20revolver%20grip%20style%20and%20rubberized%20front%20trigger%20with%20indents%20for%20your%20fingers%20make%20the%20nozzle%20as%20comfortable%20as%20it%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20ways%20to%20diversify%20your%20watering%20experience%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20customers%20complain%20of%20leakage%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20the%20inclusion%20of%20plastic%20parts.%20Overall%2C%20this%20nozzle's%20all-in-one%20design%2C%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20and%20ergonomic%20grip%20still%20earn%20it%20our%20top%20position%2C%20but%20consider%20whether%20you%20may%20prefer%20a%20more%20specialized%20nozzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20garden%20hose%20nozzle%20on%20a%20budget%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20holding%20the%20melnor%205%20pattern%20watering%20nozzle%20the%20best%20cheap%20affordable%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%202021%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6037e304bed5c50011a2c745%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20affordable%20Melnor%20offers%20all%20the%20basic%20features%20you%20need%20with%20multiple%20spray%20settings%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20most%20durable%20option.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20high-quality%20garden%20hose%20is%20an%20investment%2C%20and%20after%20spending%20that%20money%2C%20you%20might%20not%20want%20to%20splurge%20on%20an%20additional%20accessory.%20Luckily%2C%20this%20Melnor%20hose%20nozzle%20is%20very%20affordable%2C%20while%20still%20offering%20features%20you%20need%20and%20decent%20comfort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20nozzle%20keeps%20it%20simple%20with%20five%20spray%20options%20that%20should%20suit%20most%20activities%3A%20shower%2C%20full%2C%20stream%2C%20flat%2C%20and%20mist.%20All%20the%20settings%20worked%20well%20and%20had%20strong%2C%20consistent%20pressure%2C%20though%20the%20spray%20distance%20fell%20short%20compared%20to%20the%20other%20nozzles.%20The%20mist%20option%20was%20especially%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nozzle%20attached%20securely%20to%20my%20hose%2C%20but%20there%20were%20some%20small%20leaking%20issues.%20The%20droplets%20were%20tiny%20and%20didn't%20significantly%20affect%20my%20watering%20experience%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20this%20was%20the%20only%20nozzle%20I%20tested%20that%20leaked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20decently%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20rubber%20grip%20features%20indents%20for%20your%20fingers%2C%20but%20the%20back%20trigger%20section%20is%20made%20from%20plastic%20which%20is%20less%20comfortable%20than%20an%20all-rubber%20grip.%20There%20is%20a%20trigger%20lock%20to%20help%20prevent%20grip%20fatigue%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20squeeze%20down%20the%20whole%20time%20you're%20watering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20metal%2C%20plastic%2C%20and%20rubber%2C%20the%20nozzle%20is%20lightweight%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20bang%20it%20around%20the%20ground%20too%20much.%20In%20our%20durability%20tests%2C%20the%20metal%20pin%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20trigger%20lock%20fell%20out.%20While%20we%20know%20you%20won't%20purposely%20drop%20your%20nozzle%20onto%20concrete%20repeatedly%2C%20it's%20also%20good%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20this%20nozzle%20isn't%20going%20to%20last%20for%20years.%20But%20if%20you%20need%20a%20temporary%20solution%20or%20don't%20use%20your%20garden%20hose%20often%2C%20it's%20a%20quick%20and%20cheap%20buy%20with%20most%20of%20the%20features%20you%20need.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20watering%20wand%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20holding%20up%20the%20melnor%20relaxgrip%20watering%20wand%20the%20best%20garden%20hose%20watering%20wand%202021%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60