EApple%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20early%20research%20phases%20of%20building%20home%20robots.%20%3Cp%3EFernando%20Gutierrez-Juarez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20is%20exploring%20home%20robots%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20create%20its%20next%20major%20product%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20working%20on%20a%20mobile%20robot%20that%20can%20follow%20users%20and%20a%20smart%20display%20one%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20exploration%20of%20these%20devices%20comes%20after%20Apple%20killed%20its%20self-driving%20car%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20looking%20into%20making%20home%20robots%2C%20a%20move%20that%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20effort%20to%20create%20its%20%26quot%3Bnext%20big%20thing%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20killed%20its%20self-driving%20car%20project%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-04-03%2Fapple-explores-home-robots-after-abandoning-car-efforts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20are%20looking%20into%20developing%20a%20robot%20that%20could%20follow%20users%20around%20their%20houses%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20They're%20also%20exploring%20a%20tabletop%20at-home%20device%20that%20uses%20robotics%20to%20rotate%20the%20display%2C%20a%20more%20advanced%20project%20than%20the%20mobile%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20behind%20the%20smart%20display%20robot%20is%20to%20mimic%20a%20person's%20head%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20reacting%20during%20a%20FaceTime%20session.%20It%20would%20also%20include%20a%20feature%20that%20zooms%20in%20on%20a%20particular%20person%20in%20a%20crowd%20during%20a%20video%20call.%20This%20device%20initially%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20senior%20Apple%20executives%20years%20ago%2C%20though%20they've%20disagreed%20over%20whether%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20project%2C%20Bloomberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20about%20Apple's%20new%20efforts%20comes%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapples-nightmarish-year-keeps-getting-worse-doj-antitrust-iphone-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseries%20of%20recent%20blows%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20company.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20Apple%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20declining%20iPhone%20sales%20in%20China%2C%20a%20nearly%20%242%20billion%20fine%20from%20the%20EU%2C%20and%20an%20antitrust%20lawsuit%20from%20the%20DOJ.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20scrapped%20its%20decadeslong%2C%20multi-billionaire%20car%20effort%2C%20Project%20Titan%2C%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20shifting%20its%20focus%20to%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-ai-realm-resolution-conversation-understands-context-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20products.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Apple%20has%20been%20criticized%20as%20lagging%20behind%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Google%2C%20which%20have%20all%20released%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bet%20on%20home%20robots%20could%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20regain%20its%20new-product%20mojo%20eventually.%20The%20company%20reportedly%20started%20exploring%20robotics%20in%202019.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Doug%20Field%2C%20now%20an%20EV%20executive%20at%20Ford%2C%20was%20leading%20the%20project%20and%20was%20joined%20by%20leaders%20across%20the%20home%20product%20space%20to%20work%20on%20things%20like%20quiet%20indoor%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Field%20left%20the%20company%20in%202021%2C%20Bloomberg%20says%20Apple's%20robotics%20efforts%20zeroed%20in%20on%20domestic%20products.%20One%20idea%20Apple%20explored%20was%20a%20robot%20that%20could%20do%20chores%20like%20washing%20dishes%20and%20be%20used%20for%20video%20calls.%20However%2C%20the%20concept%20was%20shelved%20because%20of%20engineering%20obstacles%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20yet%20clear%20whether%20Apple's%20robots%20will%20make%20it%20to%20consumers.%20But%20Apple%20appears%20to%20have%20laid%20some%20groundwork.%20At%20least%20one%20engineer%20who%20used%20to%20be%20on%20the%20car%20project's%20hardware%20team%20has%20been%20moved%20to%20the%20home%20and%20robotics%20division%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%20Sources%20also%20say%20that%20SafetyOS%2C%20the%20operating%20system%20that%20would've%20given%20the%20car%20self-driving%20capabilities%2C%20could%20technically%20be%20repurposed%20for%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20home%20robotics%20are%20nothing%20new.%20The%20Roomba%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20a%20popular%20autonomous%20vacuum%20cleaner%20created%20by%20iRobot%20that%20Amazon%20tried%20to%20acquire%20in%202022.%20Smart%20speakers%20and%20thermostats%20are%20also%20common%20in%20people's%20homes.%20Meantime%2C%20Apple's%20latest%20non-robotic%20launch%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-returns-set-up-confusion-analyst-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20has%20had%20mixed%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20before%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-exploring-home-robots-as-next-big-thing-report-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712174869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc3cb52417f97b87ce0378%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-exploring-home-robots-as-next-big-thing-report-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20exploring%2