y%20and%20purifies%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%2C%20he%20utilises%20%3Cem%3Epanchakavya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20solution%20made%20of%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20ghee%2C%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20used%20as%20a%20fertiliser)%20spray%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20homemade%20spray%20containing%20ginger%2C%20garlic%20%26amp%3B%20chillies%20for%20controlling%20pests%20and%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20everything%20was%20going%20well%2C%20Saravanan%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle.%20Buying%20it%20from%20outside%20was%20expensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%202011%2C%20KVK%20Namakkal%20conducted%20a%20demonstration%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20hydroponic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20maize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20maize%20in%20a%20cupboard%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20696px)%20100vw%2C%20696px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20grows%20maize%20fodder%20in%20his%20cupboard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072.jpeg%20696w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-245x300.jpeg%20245w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-500x613.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-150x184.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20grows%20maize%20fodder%20in%20his%20cupboard%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fodder%20demand%20was%20increasing%20and%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20keep%20up.%20The%20existing%20land%20was%20just%20not%20sufficient%20to%20grow%20fodder.%20While%20I%20saw%20the%20demo%20in%202011%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20few%20years%20later%20that%20I%20got%20access%20to%20the%20kit%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Saravanan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Aavin%20the%20dairy%20co-operative%20in%20Namakkal%2C%20gave%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%20to%20Saravanan.%20Hydroponics%20is%20a%20technique%20of%20growing%20plants%20without%20soil%20and%20very%20little%20water.%20It%20uses%20a%20water-based%20solution%20and%20produces%20fodder%2C%20cereals%20and%20pulses%20on%20a%20small%20scale%20level.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20explains%20that%20by%20planting%20500%20gm%20of%20maize%2C%20he%20gets%204.5-5%20kg%20of%20maize%20fodder%20in%20a%20matter%20of%208%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20keep%20the%20trays%20in%20my%20cupboard%20as%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20sunlight.%20Since%20it%20grows%20in%208%20days%2C%20I%20get%20a%20sufficient%20yield%20in%20a%20month.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20pushing%20other%20farmers%20too%20to%20try%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20costs%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20explains%20the%20steps%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327478%2Fashwin-sawant-low-cost-hydroponics-model-helps-farmers-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaize%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3