.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20a%20law%20degree%2C%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20this%20case.%20From%20drafting%2C%20coordinating%20with%20the%20right%20contacts%2C%20creating%20adequate%20evidence%2C%20and%20responding%20to%20medical%20as%20well%20as%20legal%20questions%2C%20he%20meticulously%20planned%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20amend%20the%20MTP%20Act%201971.%20The%20Bill%20was%20approved%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20enhanced%20the%20upper%20gestation%20limit%20from%2020%20to%2024%20weeks%20for%20special%20categories%20of%20women%20which%20will%20be%20defined%20in%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20Act.%20It%20would%20include%20survivors%20of%20rape%2C%20victims%20of%20incest%2C%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20women%20such%20as%20disabled%20women%20and%20mi