0chance%20to%20show%20our%20hospitality%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20to%20look%20for%20places%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244062%2Fchandan-nayal-nai-gaon-uttarakhand-plant-oak-trees-deodar-regenerate-forest-quit-job-environment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Nainital%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20their%20dream%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20saw%20this%20place%2C%20it%20already%20had%20a%20wood%20structure%2C%20we%20were%20taken%20aback%20by%20its%20beauty.%20It%20has%20everything%20we%20hoped%20for.%20It%20was%20nestled%20between%20woods%20and%20two%20streams%20with%20nature%20all%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Himalaica%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20itself%20is%20in%20no%20way%20less%20captivating%20than%20the%20beauty%20around%20it.%20Made%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead%20of%20standing%20out%20as%20a%20sore%20thumb%2C%20Varun%20explains%20their%20inspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20buildings%20are%20inspired%20by%20the%20various%20Chalets%20that%20we%20visited%20in%20Switzerland.%20We%20used%20stones%20from%20the%20Kolar%20River%20nearby%20to%20make%20the%20structure.%20The%20design%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20chalets%20and%20British%20villas%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Europe.%20The%20windows%20and%20the%20doors%20are%20all%20inspired%20by%20those%20designs%20while%20using%20the%20local%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98mini-castle%E2%80%99%20hidden%20in%20the%20woods.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20factor%20while%20designing%20the%20place%20was%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20as%20close%20to%20nature%20as%20possible.%20The%20place%2C%20despite%20being%20close%20to%20Nainital%2C%20feels%20like%20we%