20stay%20as%20long%20as%20I%20wanted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20gave%20me%20the%20idea%20to%20collaborate%20with%20similar%20small%20businesses%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20the%20support%20of%20skilled%20volunteers%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20will%20get%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20offbeat%20places%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakash.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20six%20months%20of%20research%2C%20Aakash%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Karunesh%20Maan%20and%20Rakshit%20Kumar%20launched%20Volunteer%20Yatra%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20win-win%20for%20volunteers%20and%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Volunteers%20help%20hosts%20record%20good%20quality%20content%2C%20optimise%20social%20media%2C%20decorate%20property%20using%20murals%20on%20walls%2C%20and%20much%20more.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVolunteer-Yatra-3-1711769385-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5