%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20to%20Rover%20Stay%20hostel%2C%20I%20was%20their%20only%20guest%20for%20the%20next%2015%20days.%20Using%20my%20cinematic%20and%20storytelling%20skills%2C%20I%20recorded%20unique%20content%20about%20the%20region%20to%20attract%20tourists%20to%20Ghanshyam%E2%80%99s%20hostel.%20We%20also%20decorated%20domes%20using%20wall%20murals.%20All%20of%20my%20reels%20have%20crossed%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20views%20on%20Instagram.%20We%20are%20now%20working%20on%20a%20YouTube%20series%20to%20further%20attract%20tourists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20business%20observed%20growth%20after%2025%20days%2C%20for%20Prem%2C%20this%20experience%20has%20been%20extremely%20enriching%20personally.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20working%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20for%20seven%20years%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20travel.%20As%20a%20solo%20traveller%2C%20budget%20is%20always%20a%20constraint.%20But%20volunteering%20not%20only%20helped%20me%20use%20my%20skills%20for%20community%20development%20but%20also%20to%20pursue%20my%20passion.%20It%20was%20extremely%20rewarding%20to%20explore%20Rajpipla%20on%20my%20bike%20and%20record%20its%20scenic%20beauty%20on%20my%20GoPro%20and%20drone.%20I%20have%20explored%20the%20place%20more%20than%20I%20was%20expecting%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20sustain%20the%20for-profit%20business%2C%20Aakash%20charges%20an%20annual%20fee%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20from%20volunteers.%20While%20he%20charges%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20month%20from%20revenue-generating%20businesses%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20take%20no%20fee%20from%20non-profits%20and%20low-income%20businesses%20such%20as%20Ghanshyam%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20often%20I%20am%20the%20last%20person%20to%20draw%20a%20salary%20or%20sometimes%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20paid%20for%20months.%20It%20is%20tough.%2